00:20:37.650 --> 00:20:38.390 align:middle line:90%
I mean, I've seen a lot of--

00:20:38.390 --> 00:20:39.180 align:middle line:84%
>>SCRIMGEOUR: There
are a number of things.

00:20:39.180 --> 00:20:40.350 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: --adrenal
support things,

00:20:40.350 --> 00:20:41.770 align:middle line:90%
even in the health food store.

00:20:41.770 --> 00:20:42.240 align:middle line:84%
>>SCRIMGEOUR: Oh,
there are a lot

00:20:42.240 --> 00:20:43.030 align:middle line:90%
of things that are out there.

00:20:43.030 --> 00:20:44.280 align:middle line:90%
A lot of it is the potency.

00:20:44.280 --> 00:20:46.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But we want to be
looking for these things?

00:20:46.170 --> 00:20:47.310 align:middle line:84%
>>SCRIMGEOUR: Those
types of things.

00:20:47.310 --> 00:20:48.870 align:middle line:84%
The potencies are
really, really important

00:20:48.870 --> 00:20:50.670 align:middle line:84%
in terms of people accessing
that kind of stuff.

00:20:50.670 --> 00:20:51.570 align:middle line:84%
Usually, you're
going to do better

00:20:51.570 --> 00:20:53.070 align:middle line:84%
going to someone who's a
practitioner because they're

00:20:53.070 --> 00:20:55.237 align:middle line:84%
going to have a lot more
experience with that stuff.

00:20:55.237 --> 00:20:57.990 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I recently made
a formula for my patients

00:20:57.990 --> 00:20:59.720 align:middle line:84%
and for me because
I wanted to combine

00:20:59.720 --> 00:21:02.220 align:middle line:84%
all those things in there and
have a real high concentration

00:21:02.220 --> 00:21:03.390 align:middle line:90%
of the astragalus.

00:21:03.390 --> 00:21:05.160 align:middle line:10%
I wanted to put the
cordyceps in there.

00:21:05.160 --> 00:21:06.630 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to put all these
things in there that I

00:21:06.630 --> 00:21:07.740 align:middle line:90%
think are things that really--

00:21:07.740 --> 00:21:08.790 align:middle line:90%
I put Schisandra in there.

00:21:08.790 --> 00:21:10.040 align:middle line:84%
I put the Lycium,
which is like--

00:21:10.040 --> 00:21:10.220 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Oh, yeah,
which helps us sleep.

00:21:10.220 --> 00:21:12.000 align:middle line:10%
>>SCRIMGEOUR: Yeah,
the goji berries.

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:14.160 align:middle line:10%
There's a little story
in China, the guy who

00:21:14.160 --> 00:21:16.550 align:middle line:10%
