nothing but goji berries.

00:21:16.550 --> 00:21:17.967 align:middle line:10%
You know, there's
stuff like this,

00:21:17.967 --> 00:21:20.460 align:middle line:10%
but the anti-aging aspect of it.

00:21:20.460 --> 00:21:21.960 align:middle line:10%
So you want a very
balanced formula,

00:21:21.960 --> 00:21:23.998 align:middle line:10%
but you want these
things to be strong.

00:21:23.998 --> 00:21:25.540 align:middle line:84%
You want them to
really do something.

00:21:25.540 --> 00:21:26.915 align:middle line:84%
There's another
great herb called

00:21:26.915 --> 00:21:29.190 align:middle line:84%
Rehmannia, which is
not often used in terms

00:21:29.190 --> 00:21:30.352 align:middle line:90%
of these classic forms.

00:21:30.352 --> 00:21:31.560 align:middle line:90%
It's a little hard to digest.

00:21:31.560 --> 00:21:32.850 align:middle line:90%
It's really thick.

00:21:32.850 --> 00:21:35.580 align:middle line:84%
But in terms of, we would say,
kidney deficiency classically

00:21:35.580 --> 00:21:37.540 align:middle line:84%
in Chinese medicine, it's a
really, really common herb.

00:21:37.540 --> 00:21:39.110 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, let
me ask you about that.

00:21:39.110 --> 00:21:41.370 align:middle line:84%
You were talking about how
it's called kidney deficiency.

00:21:41.370 --> 00:21:41.610 align:middle line:90%
>>SCRIMGEOUR: Yes.

00:21:41.610 --> 00:21:42.410 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right?

00:21:42.410 --> 00:21:44.790 align:middle line:84%
Now, the adrenals sit
on top of the kidneys.

00:21:44.790 --> 00:21:46.090 align:middle line:90%
Is there a relationship that--

00:21:46.090 --> 00:21:47.383 align:middle line:90%
>>SCRIMGEOUR: Absolutely.

00:21:47.383 --> 00:21:49.800 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So really, we are
talking about adrenal burnout,

00:21:49.800 --> 00:21:51.342 align:middle line:84%
but what's happening
with the kidneys

00:21:51.342 --> 00:21:53.790 align:middle line:84%
that they're sitting on top
of that would maybe even be

00:21:53.790 --> 00:21:54.630 align:middle line:90%
a precursor?

00:21:54.630 --> 00:21:57.150 align:middle line:84%
>>SCRIMGEOUR: Well, the thing
is you can't necessarily

00:21:57.150 --> 00:21:58.953 align:middle line:84%
make an exact
correlation between what

00:21:58.953 --> 00:22:00.870 align:middle line:84%
we call kidney deficiency
in Chinese medicine,

00:22:00.870 --> 00:22:03.270 align:middle line:84%
or even adrenal burnout,
and kidney organ

00:22:03.270 --> 00:22:07.110 align:middle line:84%
function in Western anatomical
physiological medicine

00:22:07.110 --> 00:22:08.070 align:middle line:90%
because it's different.

00:22:08.070 --> 00:22:10.487 align:middle line:84%
In other words, it doesn't
mean you actually have a kidney

00:22:10.487 --> 00:22:12.430 align:middle line:90%
problem at all, necessarily.

00:22:12.430 --> 00:22:15.690 align:middle line:84%
So what we assign to
this kidney deficiency

00:22:15.690 --> 00:22:19.573 align:middle line:84%
is really more of an
energetic, symptomatic way

00:22:19.573 --> 00:22:21.490 align:middle line:84%
of looking at that, of
measuring what that is.

00:22:21.490 --> 00:22:23.970 align:middle line:84%
So for example, people
might have back pain.

00:22:23.970 --> 00:22:25.150 align:middle line:90%
They might have knee pain.

00:22:25.150 --> 00:22:25.980 align:middle line:90%
They might have tooth problems.

00:22:25.980 --> 00:22:27.900 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Oh, lower back pain
is like almost endemic to--

00:22:27.900 --> 00:22:29.000 align:middle line:10%
>>SCRIMGEOUR: It's
endemic, absolutely--

00:22:29.000 --> 00:22:31.770 align:middle line:10%
ear problems, with hearing
things, tinnitus, you know,

00:22:31.770 --> 00:22:32.580 align:middle line:10%
hear loss.

00:22:32.580 --> 00:22:34.788 align:middle line:10%
All these things we relate
to kidney, but also things

00:22:34.788 --> 00:22:36.714 align:middle line:10%
like willpower we
relate to kidney,

00:22:36.714 --> 00:22:38.506 align:middle line:10%
which is another one
that people experience

00:22:38.506 --> 00:22:39.060 align:middle line:10%
when they're burnt out.

00:22:39.060 --> 00:22:40.590 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Well now,
see this is a big one--

00:22:40.590 --> 00:22:40.980 align:middle line:10%
>>SCRIMGEOUR: Lack of.

00:22:40.980 --> 00:22:42.250 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: --lack of willpower.

00:22:42.250 --> 00:22:43.050 align:middle line:10%
Interesting.

00:22:43.050 --> 00:22:46.740 align:middle line:10%
So really, it's the
whole person and spirit

00:22:46.740 --> 00:22:48.000 align:middle line:10%
